ROC curve all Lasso models

plot(prf_comor1, col = "darkred")
plot(prf_comor5, add = TRUE, col = "navy")
plot(prf_comor_cov1, add = TRUE, col = "tomato")
plot(prf_comor_cov5, add = TRUE, col = "royalblue")
plot(prf_comor_cov_bio1, add = TRUE, col = "salmon")
plot(prf_comor_cov_bio5, add = TRUE, col = "skyblue")

legend("bottomright", legend = c(paste("comorbidities 1 yr, AUC = ",
round(auc_comor1, digits = 3)), paste("comorbidities 5 yrs, AUC = ",
round(auc_comor5, digits = 3)), paste("comorbidities + covariates 1 yr, AUC = ",
round(auc_comor_cov1, digits = 3)),  paste("comorbidities + covariates 5 yrs, AUC = ",
round(auc_comor_cov5, digits = 3)), paste("comorbidities + covariates + biomarkers 1 yr, AUC = ",
round(auc_comor_cov_bio1, digits = 3)), paste("comorbidities + covariates + biomarkers 5 yrs, AUC = ",
round(auc_comor_cov_bio5, digits = 3))), col = c("darkred","navy", "tomato", "royalblue", "salmon", "skyblue"), lty = 1)

Selected features by all Lasso models

features <- merge(x = coef_comor1, y = coef_comor5,  by = "non_zero_coefficients", all = TRUE)
features <- merge(x = features, y = coef_comor_cov1,  by = "non_zero_coefficients", all = TRUE)
features <- merge(x = features, y = coef_comor_cov5,  by = "non_zero_coefficients", all = TRUE)
## Warning in merge.data.frame(x = features, y = coef_comor_cov5, by =
## "non_zero_coefficients", : column names 'V1.x', 'V1.y' are duplicated in the
## result
features <- merge(x = features, y = coef_comor_cov_bio1,  by = "non_zero_coefficients", all = TRUE)
## Warning in merge.data.frame(x = features, y = coef_comor_cov_bio1, by =
## "non_zero_coefficients", : column names 'V1.x', 'V1.y' are duplicated in the
## result
features <- merge(x = features, y = coef_comor_cov_bio5,  by = "non_zero_coefficients", all = TRUE)
## Warning in merge.data.frame(x = features, y = coef_comor_cov_bio5, by =
## "non_zero_coefficients", : column names 'V1.x', 'V1.y', 'V1.x', 'V1.y' are
## duplicated in the result
colnames(features) <- c("betas","comorbidities 1 yr", "comorbidities 5 yrs", 
                        "comorbidities + covariates 1 yr",
                        "comorbidities + covariates 5 yrs",
                        "comorbidities + covariates + biomarkers 1 yr",
                        "comorbidities + covariates + biomarkers 5 yrs")

#features <- features[is.na(features)] <- 0
all_features <- features %>%
  melt(id.vars = "betas",
       variable.name = "model",
       value.name = "feature") %>%
  filter(!is.na(feature))
## Warning: attributes are not identical across measure variables; they will be
## dropped
all_features$betas <- as.numeric(levels(all_features$betas)[all_features$betas])

#%>%arrange(feature, model, beta)
ggplot(all_features, aes(fill=model, y = betas, x = feature)) +
  geom_bar(position="dodge", stat="identity") + 
  coord_cartesian(ylim=c(-1,1))

# Selected features by Lasso 1 year
